# Publish/consume @fps4/* from GitHub Packages (fps4 org). Auth is read from NODE_AUTH_TOKEN — a
# GitHub token with `packages:write` to publish (`read:packages` to install). Never commit the token
# itself; only this env reference is committed. Non-@fps4 deps still resolve from the default registry.
@fps4:registry=https://npm.pkg.github.com
//npm.pkg.github.com/:_authToken=${NODE_AUTH_TOKEN}
